        <h1 class="display-4">Privacy Statement for TicTacToeLive</h1>
        <p class="lead">Effective Date: 8/13/2023</p>
        <hr class="my-4">

        <p class="font-weight-bold">1. Data Collection and Usage</p>
        <p>We want to assure you that TicTacToeLive does not collect, store, or process any personal information. When you play the game of Tic Tac Toe on our website, we do not request, gather, or track any personally identifiable information, such as your name, email address, or contact details.</p>

        <p class="font-weight-bold">2. Usage of sessionStorage</p>
        <p>TicTacToeLive employs the use of the <code>sessionStorage</code> mechanism available in modern web browsers. This feature allows us to temporarily store data within your browser session, solely for the purpose of mediating the progress and events of the Tic Tac Toe game you play on our website. The data stored in <code>sessionStorage</code> is local to your browser and is not transmitted to our servers or any third-party services. Once you close your browser window or tab, this data is automatically cleared and no longer accessible.</p>

        <p class="font-weight-bold">3. Cookies and Tracking</p>
        <p>We do not utilize cookies or any tracking technologies to monitor your browsing activities or collect information about you on TicTacToeLive.</p>

        <p class="font-weight-bold">4. Third-Party Services</p>
        <p>TicTacToeLive does not integrate with any third-party services or platforms that might collect your personal information or track your online behavior.</p>

        <p class="font-weight-bold">5. Data Security</p>
        <p>While we do not store any personal information, we are committed to maintaining the security of the data exchanged during your interaction with our website. We implement industry-standard security measures to protect against unauthorized access, data alteration, and data loss.</p>

        <p class="font-weight-bold">6. Children's Privacy</p>
        <p>TicTacToeLive is not designed for or targeted towards individuals under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect any information from individuals under the age of 13. If you believe we may have collected information from a child under 13, please contact us so we can promptly remove the data.</p>

        <p class="font-weight-bold">7. Changes to the Privacy Statement</p>
        <p>TicTacToeLive may update this Privacy Statement from time to time. Any changes to the statement will be posted on this page with an updated effective date. We encourage you to review this statement periodically to stay informed about how we are protecting your privacy.</p>

        <p class="font-weight-bold">8. Contact Us</p>
        <p>If you have any questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Statement or your interactions with TicTacToeLive, please contact us at neilj1213@outlook.com.</p>

        <p>By using TicTacToeLive, you agree to the practices outlined in this Privacy Statement. Thank you for trusting us with your privacy as you enjoy playing Tic Tac Toe on our platform.</p>
